    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>It got deprecated in version <code>4.3-alpha1</code> which you use because of the <code>LATEST</code> version specification. If you take a look at the javadoc of the class, it tells you what to use instead: <code>HttpClientBuilder</code>.</p>\n\n<p>In the latest stable version (<code>4.2.3</code>) the <code>DefaultHttpClient</code> is not deprecated yet.</p>\n"
  }, {
