    "answer_id" : 15336663,
    "question_id" : 15336477,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Use <a href=\"http://hc.apache.org/httpcomponents-client-dev/httpclient/apidocs/org/apache/http/impl/client/HttpClientBuilder.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">HttpClientBuilder</a> to build the <a href=\"http://hc.apache.org/httpcomponents-client-dev/httpclient/apidocs/org/apache/http/client/HttpClient.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">HttpClient</a> instead of using DefaultHttpClient</p>\n\n<p>ex:</p>\n\n<pre><code>MinimalHttpClient httpclient = new HttpClientBuilder().build();\n\n // Prepare a request object\n HttpGet httpget = new HttpGet(\"http://www.apache.org/\");\n</code></pre>\n"
